  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Infinite Idle: Online Clicker RPG</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>They will never give up with dozens of different enemies and bosses! This battle will continue forever. Get ready to fight with better decisions each time.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3197860/extras/76d53b19eb3f2ae39efe4f9440b3d207.avif?t=1732227172\" width=572 height=152 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Make the best decisions from dozens of different options. There will be surprise gifts and helpers for you, don't forget to use them. Remember, you can't take gold home.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3197860/extras/16fcc9361c54304a506dab3c025d0809.avif?t=1732227172\" width=572 height=152 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Use your special abilities to overcome impassable difficulties with a good strategy. The battle continues even when you are not there. Don't forget this! Always stronger when you are there.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3197860/extras/1d3703f17b17108f744cbbc0bd40fd52.poster.avif?t=1732227172\" width=572 height=228 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3197860/extras/1d3703f17b17108f744cbbc0bd40fd52.webm?t=1732227172\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3197860/extras/1d3703f17b17108f744cbbc0bd40fd52.mp4?t=1732227172\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Infinite Idle: Online Clicker RPG</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>They will never give up with dozens of different enemies and bosses! This battle will continue forever. Get ready to fight with better decisions each time.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3197860/extras/76d53b19eb3f2ae39efe4f9440b3d207.avif?t=1732227172\" width=572 height=152 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Make the best decisions from dozens of different options. There will be surprise gifts and helpers for you, don't forget to use them. Remember, you can't take gold home.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3197860/extras/16fcc9361c54304a506dab3c025d0809.avif?t=1732227172\" width=572 height=152 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Use your special abilities to overcome impassable difficulties with a good strategy. The battle continues even when you are not there. Don't forget this! Always stronger when you are there.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3197860/extras/1d3703f17b17108f744cbbc0bd40fd52.poster.avif?t=1732227172\" width=572 height=228 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3197860/extras/1d3703f17b17108f744cbbc0bd40fd52.webm?t=1732227172\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3197860/extras/1d3703f17b17108f744cbbc0bd40fd52.mp4?t=1732227172\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
